description: Replace your broken or scratched Blu ray boxes and keep your collection looking nice!These are the same size as the translucent blue boxes that come with Blu ray movies you buy them in the store! These replacement Blu ray boxes come with full wrap-around sleeve, so you have a protected spot for the DVD insert sheet!The cases are 12mm thick -- slightly thinner than a standard DVD case -- and have the Blu ray logo on the outside at the top. They have two clips on the inside to hold additional booklets.These are just like the cases you buy with normal Blu ray Discs.  If yours are getting scratched and unpleasant looking, you can switch the paper and disc to these new ones and spruce up your collection.  Or, if you're starting to record and burn your own HD home videos to Blu ray, use this case to store and protect your discs, and give them the authentic Blu ray look.
title: Empty Standard Blue Replacement Boxes / Cases for Blu-ray Disc Movies DVBR12BR-10 boxes
